区，同时也促进人员流动。 在 4 月 3 日和 4 日的美股暴跌中，美国七大科技股的市值蒸发了 1.6 万亿美元，科技富豪们的财富也大幅缩水。根据彭博富豪榜 6 日数据，马斯克过去两天净资产缩水超过 300 亿美元，全球首富排行榜位居第二和第三位的亚马逊创始人贝佐斯和「元」公司创始人扎克伯格的净资产也分别蒸发 235 亿美元和 273 亿美元。全球前三大富豪过去两天净资产合计蒸发了超过 800 亿美元。 更多资讯请下载央视新闻客户端"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c89ed9b5dcaa537b1bc6603c237c3dc2_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "411 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1892859093955343432"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIk4+B4NPww4RJEAMaCTExNDM4Mzg1MSDH4NG/BjAAOP4BQANyEzE4OTI4NTkwOTM5NTUzNDM0MzJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1744086512.920895", "card_id": "Q_1892335819433406884", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 28}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待朝鲜时隔 6 年再办国际马拉松赛，男女全马冠军均由朝鲜选手获得？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "当地时间 4 月 6 日，第 31 届平壤国际马拉松赛在朝鲜举行。这是朝鲜时隔六年再次办赛。 朝鲜选手朴金东以 2 小时 12 分 11 秒的成绩获取男子全程马拉松第一名，朝鲜选手全秀景以 2 小时 25 分 50 秒的成绩摘得女子全程马拉松冠军。 时隔六年 朝鲜再次举行国际马拉松赛"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-5975396a2ece1938c076a7850d689c18_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "227 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1892335819433406884"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIk4+B4NPww4RJEAMaCTExNDM2MTk4NCDxkcq/BjAAOD5ABHITMTg5MjMzNTgxOTQzMzQwNjg4NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1744086512.922238", "card_id": "Q_1892873920669012862", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night